pageContext.claim: “Eliminate America's borders in the middle of a pandemic yet. [Biden] wants to tear down the wall, he actually suggested tearing down the wall that we fought so hard to get built.”
pageContext.analysis: False. Biden has stated in no uncertain terms that he would not take down the portions of the border fencing system Trump has built, although he would stop further construction. “There will not be another foot of wall constructed on my administration,” Biden told NPR.
